    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spectral Prison是一款恐怖游戏，在游戏中，你将置身一栋房子里，被困在循环中，而这栋房子似乎会随着邪恶典狱长的意志而改变，让你永远无法逃脱。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >被困</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >David Echo在一间昏暗的卧室中醒来，这是这所令人感觉异常扭曲的房子中唯一熟悉的地方。你的目标？找到钥匙打开房门，逃出这座幽灵监狱。但要小心，房子里可能处处有“雷”。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以为自己终于逃出来了？那可就大错特错了。邪恶的典狱长监视着你的一举一动，随时准备抓住你，把你送到更可怕的空间里。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >典狱长之怒</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >典狱长不喜欢你以牙还牙将他击败，他会想方设法增加每个循环的难度，试图让你放弃，留在他的监狱里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/aaf8c27f69f388e37085fb2e15b2971e.poster.avif?t=1749656796\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/aaf8c27f69f388e37085fb2e15b2971e.webm?t=1749656796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/aaf8c27f69f388e37085fb2e15b2971e.mp4?t=1749656796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >不断变化的房子</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每次你回来时，房子都会发生变化。钥匙的位置会改变，因为典狱长试图将你一直关在房子里。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/d2575399a89dad43cd3878c1fc9086c6.poster.avif?t=1749656796\" width=768 height=432 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/d2575399a89dad43cd3878c1fc9086c6.webm?t=1749656796\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3264760/extras/d2575399a89dad43cd3878c1fc9086c6.mp4?t=1749656796\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p>",
